phrases: Well then, I will be taking some meat again!
Your tail is going to disappear before long.
Looks like you have gotten a little bit better.
Wow, to think that Kami- sama is going to be training us!
Damn, I am just itching all over!
Take it easy, take it easy.
In any case, we have to find Tenshinhan and Chaozu.
Those two are going to be so surprised!
Yamucha- sama, after you and everyone else have Kami- sama make you stronger,
those Saiyans will be nothing to you!
If you are coming, then bring it on, Saiyans!
Have we arrived at Earth already?
I thought we might stop off on the way, and set my wake-up timer.
There is a pretty good planet ahead of us.
We can sell it for a lot!
Sleeping for one year straight gets you all out of form, so this will be perfect!
You are sure we can sell a place like this for a high price?
They look like they are space men.
To think that we would come across space men on our hunt!
I am sure that Moai- sama will be pleased!
You have come all the way from outer space.
Let us let them introduce us to this Moai.
Do not scare us like that!
This money is a present for Ten- san!
You guys stay out of it!
I will feed you all kinds of nutritious things with this money!
Behave yourselves for a little while now, space men.
It looks like quite an enjoyable little planet, huh?
I have never seen any before!
Never mind, he is now finally started reaching out after space men.
How far is he going to go before he is satisfied?
You have come to this planet at a bad time.
Ever since Moai has claimed the throne, things have been crazy.
Everyone in the general population has become Moai's toys!
And as for me, I had my wife stolen from me on our wedding day!
Do you understand how I feel?
Do not tell me you are still thinking about that other man.
I- I do not want to die!
You say you have captured some space men?
If they are cute, I will make them my pets.
C- could they be the ones?
How did they get out of the prison?
W- what power those guys have!
There is no way I can keep them as pets.
How would you like to make a wager with me?
Have a go at fighting against my warriors.
If you win, I will give you anything you like.
Although, no matter how you look at it, there is no chance of you beating them.
I would like to see what kind of blood is spilled by space men.
What the hell's going on here?
You said you would give us anything we liked, right?
We are taking this planet, and your lives!
Do not you get it yet?
We let ourselves be captured on purpose.
In order for us to be led in here, you see.
Are not I at Kaio- sama's place yet!?
So this monster is your ace in the hole, huh?
You intend to test your strength against Yedi's!?
You are indeed the saviors of this planet!
Peace is sure to return to this planet now, just as it was before!
We will not be able to get squat for this planet.
Get out of my sight, you good-for-nothing planet!
They are beautiful when they are obliterated, no matter what planet they happen to be.
Still, I hope this Earth turns out to be a little bit better of a planet than this.
Hey, if it turns out to be another good-for-nothing planet,
we will just blow it away too.
After we have gathered those Dragon Ball things, that is.
I am looking forward to that!
ls there any future for earth?
Elsewhere, Goku single-mindedly continues to run in order to meet Kaio-sama.
